{"tid":929697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大預言家何志平：出得嚟行預咗要還","createTime":"2018-12-05T20:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T10:23:25.000Z","uid":45657,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e09ac7a2314ee3b3f3bc9194b3bb8e8cd5dc89a","tid":929697,"uid":45657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T20:03:03.000Z","msg":"2016年，何志平加入「公職人員誠信關注組有限公司」擔任名譽主席，他表示每一個人應有誠信，包括公務員，更指出誠信是中華民族的核心價值觀，公職人員收取黑金<span style=\"color: red;\">「出得嚟行預咗要還」</span>（出來混，遲早要還的）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181206/58997270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F58997270&d=zGmyZrjC1OuOnOgxBhMVIQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=20fafbdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F58997270&h=fc8e1b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181206/58997270</a><br />\n<br />\n陪審團經歷約4小時商討，美國紐約時間下午2時左右，陪審團已有結果，何志平被控的8項控罪當中，有7項一致通過罪名成立，最高刑罰為入獄65年，最高合共罰款165萬美元。法官將於明年3月判刑。<br />\n<br />\n何志平聽完判決之後，保持微笑 ，神情沒有太大變化，並跟辯護律師逐一握手。當記者上前問他心情如何時，他回答：「預咗，都係咁」，然後記者再追問他會否上訴，他沒有回應，再有記者問他有甚麼說話向香港人說，他說：「多謝」。辯方律師Edward Kim就對記者提問有關上訴，以及要求判刑年期都不作回應。"},{"pid":"6e6b8ba608ba208f472bba0484d9d8ff5bfb2a83","tid":929697,"uid":79410,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T20:05:12.000Z","msg":"幾時到老懵懂, 689<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8524771108e06fa5be7b30b851043c91d4339c1","tid":929697,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T20:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ab66f3b4ee85b503e88b8